        <div class="quote">"</div>
		 <p class="press-preview-text">There is a deep ancestral history behind gua sha... it was a way to respect and acknowledge my heritage. This isn't a means of capitalistic gain for me, it’s an authentic dimension of my past. Because of this, it hurts to see gua sha be appropriated and cheapened so much. </p>
