        <div class="quote">"</div>
        <div class="press-preview-text"> Lin Chen is carving out her own path in the natural beauty industry, one that is unique to her skillsets and identity as a Taiwanese-American woman.<br><br> “I’m definitely really proud of myself,” said Chen. “It has taken me a long time to get to where I am and who I am today. I was taking these small steps to building my own life and building a foundation for myself.”</div>
        <p class="date spacing--3">- Jun. 2018</p>
        <img class="logo" src='{{'pbp_logo.png' | asset_url }}' />
